  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bca\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb5\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd : \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b95\u0ba8\u0baa\u0bb0\u0bc8 14 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Attack on Kilinochchi Regional Health Services Director: 14 days interrogation of suspect",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kilinochchi District Magistrate's Court has ordered that the suspect who attempted to attack the Kilinochchi Regional Health Services Director be remanded for the next 14 days.",
        "An attempt was made to attack the Regional Health Services Director Saravana Bhavan by a person while refueling in the Kilinochchi District last (23).",
        "The suspect who attempted to carry out the attack was arrested by the Kilinochchi Police and produced before the Kilinochchi District Magistrate's Court yesterday and has been remanded for 14 days.",
        "He was arrested on charges of obstruction of state duty and attempted assault on a government official.",
        "Despite the shortage of doctors and other obstacles, especially in the Kilinochchi district, the health department has been relentlessly providing other public servants with the task of preventing illegal sand mining crews and hoarders from interfering with such authorities and preventing them from obtaining fuel. It is noteworthy that this incident took place on the spot."
      ],
